title: Electric's VOLT-O for the THRILLS x STAB MAGAZINE DEMOLITION
description: Electric have transformed their 1983 Volvo wagon into the VOLT-O for the upcoming THRILLS x STAB MAGAZINE Demolition Derby this Saturday the 26th of November at Archerfield International Speedway.Stay tuned for part 3 from the race night!
